Welcome on Logram !


I. HOW TO GET LOGRAM ?

If you want install Logram, you need :
	- libqt4-dev >= 4.4 (4.5 recommanded)
	- libphonon4
	- libphonon-dev

Checkout the latest version of Logram via the SVN repository :
	$ svn co svn://logram-project.org/logram/trunk
And update it with :
	$ svn update


II. HOW TO INSTALL LOGRAM ?

In the trunk folder, just run with the superuser privileges :
	# make
	# make install


III. HOW TO TEST LOGRAM ?

If you want test on a real X-Server, just laucnh this commands :
	$ X :1 &		# You can change :1
	$ export DISPLAY=:1
	$ panache-wm &
	$ panache-desktop &

If you want to test in a virtual X-Server, you need Xephyr :
	$ Xephyr :1 -ac -kb -screen 800x600 &
	$ export DISPLAY=:1
	$ panache-wm &
	$ panache-desktop &

And enjoy with Logram
